473
00:20:31,200 --> 00:20:31,920
Go to Mr. Wen.

474
00:20:32,030 --> 00:20:32,640
Talk to him.

475
00:20:33,920 --> 00:20:34,350
Alright!

476
00:20:35,830 --> 00:20:36,550
Thank you, Ms. Fang!

477
00:20:56,720 --> 00:20:57,200
Juan.

478
00:20:58,160 --> 00:20:59,070
(I saw Agent Wu showing)

479
00:20:59,070 --> 00:21:00,070
