480
00:21:00,400 --> 00:21:01,270
(I was taking a walk.)

481
00:21:01,400 --> 00:21:02,440
(They were looking at 2708.)

482
00:21:03,440 --> 00:21:04,590
Hao Qianqian's house?

483
