546
00:23:39,590 --> 00:23:40,830
As I remember, she is

547
00:23:41,110 --> 00:23:42,200
hardworking and professional.

548
00:23:42,240 --> 00:23:42,830
Indeed.

549
00:23:44,790 --> 00:23:46,000
If she could just focus

550
00:23:46,000 --> 00:23:47,270
on her insurance business,

551
00:23:47,550 --> 00:23:48,640
