554
00:23:52,750 --> 00:23:53,510
But Qian...

555
00:23:55,960 --> 00:23:56,510
I see.

556
00:23:57,110 --> 00:23:58,160
As long as it's not

557
00:23:58,200 --> 00:23:59,310
