562
00:24:14,110 --> 00:24:14,750
Thanks to you,

563
00:24:14,790 --> 00:24:16,400
I closed a huge deal.

564
00:24:16,440 --> 00:24:18,440
Oh my, why are you thanking me?

565
00:24:18,750 --> 00:24:19,590
You introduced

566
00:24:19,590 --> 00:24:20,880
Wen Liang to us before.

567
00:24:20,960 --> 00:24:22,510
He needs insurance services,

568
00:24:22,640 --> 00:24:23,480
