569
00:24:23,790 --> 00:24:24,830
It has nothing to do with me.

570
00:24:25,830 --> 00:24:26,830
Anyway,

571
00:24:26,830 --> 00:24:28,720
I'm really happy today.

572
00:24:28,750 --> 00:24:29,550
Can't believe the client

573
00:24:29,750 --> 00:24:31,960
I've chased for a decade

574
00:24:32,110 --> 00:24:33,400
