624
00:26:13,160 --> 00:26:13,550
Ms. Fang.

625
00:26:13,830 --> 00:26:14,270
Mr. Wen.

626
00:26:14,440 --> 00:26:15,160
Have you read

627
00:26:15,200 --> 00:26:15,920
