just alright.

632
00:26:21,510 --> 00:26:22,590
It's incredibly imaginative!

633
00:26:22,960 --> 00:26:23,550
I've always hoped

634
00:26:23,590 --> 00:26:24,720
to see a design like this.

635
00:26:24,960 --> 00:26:25,550
I've sent it

636
00:26:25,590 --> 00:26:26,240
to the distributors

637
