for feedback.

638
00:26:27,110 --> 00:26:28,030
They're all very pleased.

639
00:26:29,400 --> 00:26:30,350
Which designer

640
00:26:30,400 --> 00:26:31,240
created this?

641
00:26:31,440 --> 00:26:32,270
It's from Mr. Gao's

642
00:26:32,440 --> 00:26:33,720
independent studio.

643
00:26:35,590 --> 00:26:36,110
I see.

644
00:26:36,310 --> 00:26:37,000
Go ahead, Mr. Wen.

645
00:26:37,030 --> 00:26:37,400
Okay.

646
00:26:45,440 --> 00:26:46,440
Is it inappropriate to go

647
00:26:46,440 --> 00:26:47,550
hiking during work hours?

648
00:26:48,350 --> 00:26:50,240
