Juan!

683
00:28:02,200 --> 00:28:02,960
What happened?

684
00:28:03,200 --> 00:28:04,480
I don't know what she was thinking.

685
00:28:05,110 --> 00:28:06,000
She didn't even tell us

686
00:28:06,110 --> 00:28:07,000
