687
00:28:07,200 --> 00:28:08,400
She only called me because

688
00:28:08,590 --> 00:28:10,070
there was no one
to sign the consent form.

689
00:28:10,640 --> 00:28:11,480
What does she have?

690
00:28:11,960 --> 00:28:12,550
Cancer.

691
00:28:13,270 --> 00:28:14,240
The doctor said that

692
00:28:14,590 --> 00:28:16,030
luckily, it was caught early.

693
00:28:20,680 --> 00:28:21,680
Liu Zhu?

694
00:28:25,550 --> 00:28:26,310
Zhu...

695
00:28:32,000 --> 00:28:32,880
Don't worry.

696
00:28:34,200 --> 00:28:35,590
I'll look after her for life.

697
00:28:42,240 --> 00:28:43,920
When Qian called me,

698
00:28:44,240 --> 00:28:45,440
I was at the canteen.

699
00:28:46,440 --> 00:28:47,110
So I came

700
00:28:47,160 --> 00:28:48,030
