701
00:28:48,440 --> 00:28:49,640
I had to be here.

702
00:28:50,920 --> 00:28:52,070
She's Dahu's mother.

703
00:28:53,830 --> 00:28:54,880
And I'm his father.

704
00:28:57,550 --> 00:28:58,030
We...

705
00:29:01,270 --> 00:29:02,590
We're family.

706
00:29:07,750 --> 00:29:08,920
Family of Hao Qianqian?

707
00:29:12,480 --> 00:29:13,160
Qian?

708
00:29:13,640 --> 00:29:14,590
Qian? Qian?

709
00:29:15,240 --> 00:29:15,960
Qian?

710
