Only two family members allowed.

713
00:29:34,830 --> 00:29:35,310
Oh, okay.

714
00:29:35,920 --> 00:29:36,350
Stay here.

715
00:29:37,160 --> 00:29:37,830
Let them go.

716
00:29:44,030 --> 00:29:45,000
Hey, where are you going?

717
00:29:45,510 --> 00:29:46,200
