718
00:29:46,400 --> 00:29:47,070
I'll buy something.

719
00:29:47,200 --> 00:29:47,830
No need.

720
00:29:48,310 --> 00:29:49,480
She's just undergone surgery.

721
00:29:49,510 --> 00:29:50,200
She can only

722
00:29:50,310 --> 00:29:51,110
have liquids.

723
