The hospital will provide.

724
00:29:52,240 --> 00:29:52,790
Yes, yes...

725
00:29:54,920 --> 00:29:56,680
Then someone needs
to stay with her at night.

726
00:29:57,000 --> 00:29:57,750
Fang Wanzhi and Li Juan

727
00:29:57,750 --> 00:29:58,830
are already exhausted enough.

728
00:29:59,000 --> 00:29:59,720
We can't let them...

729
00:29:59,880 --> 00:30:01,000
Even if they can't stay with her,

730
00:30:01,070 --> 00:30:02,200
there are still caregivers.

731
00:30:02,680 --> 00:30:03,350
Don't worry.

732
00:30:07,830 --> 00:30:08,440
Then...

733
00:30:08,680 --> 00:30:09,750
What can I do to help?

734
00:30:15,350 --> 00:30:17,680
You shouldn't have
told Liu Zhu about this.

735
00:30:19,030 --> 00:30:20,790
If I had known, I would have

736
