called Wanzhi.

737
00:30:22,510 --> 00:30:23,960
I got anxious when I heard you were

738
00:30:23,960 --> 00:30:24,830
going to have surgery.

739
00:30:25,350 --> 00:30:26,680
Zhu was really worried about you.

740
00:30:27,590 --> 00:30:29,400
He said he'd look after you for life.

741
00:30:32,200 --> 00:30:34,440
I'm not bedridden.

742
00:30:35,030 --> 00:30:36,310
I don't need him to look after me.

743
00:30:37,110 --> 00:30:38,110
Alright now.

744
00:30:39,070 --> 00:30:40,400
You just had surgery.

745
00:30:40,830 --> 00:30:41,640
Stop talking.

746
00:30:41,790 --> 00:30:43,070
Juan only means well.

747
00:30:43,680 --> 00:30:44,590
Don't blame her.

748
00:30:45,640 --> 00:30:47,750
Good intentions can still go wrong.

749
00:30:48,480 --> 00:30:50,550
In my condition right now,

750
00:30:51,240 --> 00:30:53,510
the last person I want to see is him.

751
00:30:55,030 --> 00:30:56,000
I look so pathetic.

752
00:31:00,200 --> 00:31:01,160
Wanzhi,

753
00:31:02,790 --> 00:31:04,480
can I ask you for a favor?

754
00:31:05,510 --> 00:31:06,070
Just tell me.

755
00:31:07,680 --> 00:31:09,000
Give Liu Zhu

756
00:31:09,680 --> 00:31:11,640
