760
00:31:21,880 --> 00:31:23,590
and have some fun the next day.

761
00:31:24,510 --> 00:31:27,000
Then, send Dahu straight

762
00:31:27,030 --> 00:31:28,640
to school on Monday.

763
00:31:31,070 --> 00:31:33,200
Tell him to keep quiet about it.

764
00:31:34,550 --> 00:31:36,880
Don't tell Dahu that I'm sick.

765
00:31:38,240 --> 00:31:39,510
As for me,

766
00:31:39,920 --> 00:31:41,240
I'll be discharged

767
