768
00:31:43,160 --> 00:31:44,480
A week?

769
00:31:45,720 --> 00:31:47,070
It won't be that fast.

770
00:31:47,400 --> 00:31:48,070
Qian,

771
00:31:49,480 --> 00:31:50,350
don't push yourself.

772
00:31:51,400 --> 00:31:53,200
I can choose not to.

773
00:31:55,640 --> 00:31:57,200
But facing my son,

774
00:32:00,030 --> 00:32:01,240
I need to stay strong.

775
00:32:02,400 --> 00:32:04,000
I'm afraid he'll feel inferior.

776
00:32:05,310 --> 00:32:07,160
I don't want him to feel

777
00:32:09,400 --> 00:32:12,200
