780
00:32:26,590 --> 00:32:27,400
I understand.

781
00:32:28,310 --> 00:32:30,550
You must keep Liu Zhu in check.

782
00:32:33,200 --> 00:32:35,880
If you spill the beans,

783
00:32:36,830 --> 00:32:37,680
