784
00:32:40,550 --> 00:32:41,240
Fine.

785
00:32:41,550 --> 00:32:42,200
Rest assured.

786
00:32:42,310 --> 00:32:43,590
I know what to do.

787
00:32:44,510 --> 00:32:45,590
Go on, get some rest.

788
00:32:46,550 --> 00:32:48,400
Take a good rest now.

789
00:32:58,680 --> 00:32:59,440
I really

790
