793
00:33:05,550 --> 00:33:06,550
to try to set them up.

794
00:33:07,270 --> 00:33:08,480
I didn't think much of it.

795
00:33:10,350 --> 00:33:11,400
You meant well.

796
00:33:14,510 --> 00:33:15,640
You should go tell Liu Zhu

797
00:33:16,240 --> 00:33:17,350
