800
00:33:22,720 --> 00:33:23,310
Okay.

801
00:33:29,000 --> 00:33:29,550
Hello.

802
00:33:29,920 --> 00:33:30,590
Noodles, please.

803
00:33:31,310 --> 00:33:31,920
No noodles today.

804
00:33:32,590 --> 00:33:34,480
Is the noodle shop closed again today?

805
00:33:35,110 --> 00:33:36,720
Chef Liu didn't leave, did he?

806
00:33:39,640 --> 00:33:40,960
Hello, a bowl of noodles, please.

807
00:33:41,790 --> 00:33:43,240
I told you, no noodles today!

808
00:33:43,720 --> 00:33:45,070
Fine, no need to be so harsh.

809
00:33:52,350 --> 00:33:53,640
Why talk to the workers like that?

810
00:33:57,070 --> 00:33:58,070
I'm sorry, Ms. Li.

811
00:33:58,720 --> 00:33:59,510
It won't happen again.

812
00:34:01,640 --> 00:34:02,790
Why isn't Liu Zhu at work today?

813
00:34:04,590 --> 00:34:05,830
He's been taking leave every day

814
00:34:06,440 --> 00:34:08,000
to bring meals to
his ex-wife at the hospital.

815
00:34:08,440 --> 00:34:09,710
The manager said that if it happens

816
00:34:09,920 --> 00:34:10,630
again tomorrow,

817
00:34:10,710 --> 00:34:11,630
he'll be fired,

818
00:34:13,000 --> 00:34:14,510
no matter who he knows.

819
00:34:15,630 --> 00:34:17,230
You don't want Liu Zhu to leave?

820
00:34:19,880 --> 00:34:20,710
It's not like that.

821
00:34:22,230 --> 00:34:23,400
I just feel

822
00:34:24,280 --> 00:34:25,710
Chef Liu is really skilled.

823
00:34:26,960 --> 00:34:27,920
And he's a nice man.

824
00:34:28,840 --> 00:34:30,280
Losing his job like this

825
00:34:30,480 --> 00:34:31,480
is really a shame.

826
00:34:42,320 --> 00:34:42,920
Zhu.

827
00:34:45,400 --> 00:34:46,000
Ms. Li,

828
00:34:46,590 --> 00:34:47,280
you came.

829
00:34:48,550 --> 00:34:49,360
Please help me

830
00:34:49,480 --> 00:34:50,670
take this meal to Qian.

831
00:34:51,230 --> 00:34:52,670
It's visiting hours now.

832
00:34:54,030 --> 00:34:55,440
Why don't you go in yourself?

833
00:34:56,880 --> 00:34:57,760
