834
00:34:58,630 --> 00:35:00,070
She even asked the nurses to stop me.

835
00:35:01,150 --> 00:35:02,880
So they're blocking me from going in.

836
00:35:03,440 --> 00:35:04,030
Juan,

837
00:35:04,800 --> 00:35:06,480
could you please put in
a good word for me

838
00:35:06,480 --> 00:35:07,360
so I can see her?

839
00:35:08,030 --> 00:35:09,320
I'm worried about her.

840
00:35:10,030 --> 00:35:11,030
He's here again?

841
00:35:14,230 --> 00:35:16,280
Did you really have to go as far

842
00:35:16,320 --> 00:35:18,030
as asking the nurses to block him?

843
00:35:18,590 --> 00:35:19,840
Why?

844
00:35:20,070 --> 00:35:21,480
Even if you two aren't a couple now,

845
