846
00:35:22,880 --> 00:35:23,760
Besides, a complete...

847
00:35:23,760 --> 00:35:24,360
Besides what?

848
00:35:24,400 --> 00:35:26,000
I know what you want to say.

849
00:35:26,190 --> 00:35:27,480
You want to tell me

850
00:35:28,030 --> 00:35:29,280
that he's Dahu's father,

851
00:35:29,400 --> 00:35:30,880
and I'm Dahu's mother.

852
00:35:31,150 --> 00:35:32,280
So what?

853
00:35:33,230 --> 00:35:35,400
There's nothing between us anymore.

854
00:35:35,630 --> 00:35:37,110
He just wants to see you.

855
00:35:37,880 --> 00:35:39,710
He'll be at ease after seeing you.

856
00:35:42,070 --> 00:35:43,150
I'll go see him.

857
00:35:43,800 --> 00:35:45,320
Go where? Lie down.

858
00:35:47,760 --> 00:35:49,630
The doctor mentioned it during rounds

859
00:35:49,630 --> 00:35:50,800
this morning.

860
00:35:51,110 --> 00:35:53,110
I need to get up and walk around more

861
00:35:53,150 --> 00:35:54,070
