862
00:35:57,920 --> 00:35:58,920
Don't follow me.

863
00:36:21,670 --> 00:36:22,280
Qian...

864
00:36:25,920 --> 00:36:26,550
Finished eating?

865
00:36:35,070 --> 00:36:35,800
You haven't eaten?

866
00:36:36,670 --> 00:36:38,030
I made your favorite.

867
00:36:38,230 --> 00:36:39,230
It's been years.

868
00:36:40,280 --> 00:36:41,400
My tastes have changed.

869
00:36:42,360 --> 00:36:43,480
What do you like to eat now?

870
00:36:44,230 --> 00:36:45,110
I'll make it tomorrow.

871
00:36:45,110 --> 00:36:45,920
Tomorrow?

872
00:36:47,710 --> 00:36:48,630
Have you no shame?

873
00:36:51,110 --> 00:36:51,710
Qian...

874
00:36:54,000 --> 00:36:55,070
It was my fault before.

875
00:36:56,000 --> 00:36:57,000
I was such a jerk.

876
00:36:58,190 --> 00:36:58,960
I apologize.

877
00:37:02,400 --> 00:37:03,840
Now that you're in this condition,

878
00:37:04,880 --> 00:37:06,360
