879
00:37:06,920 --> 00:37:07,440
After all,

880
00:37:08,030 --> 00:37:08,590
Dahu,

881
00:37:09,880 --> 00:37:10,400
you,

882
00:37:11,400 --> 00:37:12,000
and me...

883
00:37:13,710 --> 00:37:14,400
The three...

884
00:37:15,670 --> 00:37:17,360
The three of us make a complete family.

885
00:37:24,800 --> 00:37:26,030
What "condition" am I in?

886
00:37:30,320 --> 00:37:32,030
