887
00:37:34,550 --> 00:37:36,230
Get up right now!

888
00:37:44,590 --> 00:37:47,150
It ended between us a long time ago.

889
00:37:48,960 --> 00:37:50,710
You can't even accept

890
00:37:50,760 --> 00:37:51,880
such a simple fact?

891
00:37:53,880 --> 00:37:55,280
How could Dahu have such

892
00:37:55,440 --> 00:37:57,190
a cowardly father like you?

893
00:37:59,920 --> 00:38:01,280
You've been good to me before.

894
00:38:03,550 --> 00:38:05,150
And I haven't really wronged you.

895
00:38:06,150 --> 00:38:07,550
But if you keep pestering me,

896
00:38:08,000 --> 00:38:09,190
you'll ruin the last bit

897
00:38:09,320 --> 00:38:10,590
of good memories we have.

898
00:38:11,960 --> 00:38:12,550
Qian,

899
00:38:14,070 --> 00:38:14,710
don't get angry.

900
00:38:14,710 --> 00:38:16,030
I'm not angry.

901
00:38:19,670 --> 00:38:21,800
Go live your own life.

902
00:38:23,110 --> 00:38:23,760
Otherwise,

903
00:38:26,960 --> 00:38:30,070
I'll never respect you again.

904
00:39:12,030 --> 00:39:12,880
Take it slow.

905
00:39:15,190 --> 00:39:16,320
Take him back with you.

906
00:39:17,440 --> 00:39:18,590
Tell him

907
00:39:19,670 --> 00:39:21,880
that although jobs are easy
to find in Shenzhen,

908
00:39:22,800 --> 00:39:24,150
at his age,

909
00:39:24,230 --> 00:39:25,440
he has no advantage.

910
00:39:26,440 --> 00:39:28,440
If he doesn't cherish this job,

911
00:39:29,150 --> 00:39:30,670
he won't be able
to establish a foothold.

912
00:39:32,550 --> 00:39:33,440
Then,

913
00:39:34,280 --> 00:39:35,800
he will never see Dahu again.

914
00:39:40,760 --> 00:39:41,840
That's too harsh.

915
00:39:42,630 --> 00:39:43,510
I can't say that.

916
00:39:46,360 --> 00:39:47,280
You have to.

917
00:39:48,960 --> 00:39:51,190
And you need to be even harsher.

918
00:39:58,480 --> 00:39:59,320
Please.

919
00:40:59,280 --> 00:40:59,760
Juan?

920
00:40:59,760 --> 00:41:00,440
You're back.

921
00:41:02,400 --> 00:41:03,670
Go sit down and have a rest.

922
00:41:03,840 --> 00:41:05,110
The meal's ready in ten minutes.

923
00:41:07,400 --> 00:41:08,230
No need to rush.

924
00:41:08,480 --> 00:41:09,440
I'm not hungry.

925
00:41:10,960 --> 00:41:12,510
Let the three of us

926
00:41:12,960 --> 00:41:13,800
talk privately.

927
00:41:15,190 --> 00:41:15,630
Fine.

928
00:41:20,280 --> 00:41:20,760
Easy.

929
00:41:28,960 --> 00:41:30,070
You're so impressive,

930
00:41:30,760 --> 00:41:32,030
being discharged in two weeks.

931
00:41:32,960 --> 00:41:34,590
It's the weekend today.

932
00:41:34,760 --> 00:41:36,070
My son's coming home.

933
00:41:36,630 --> 00:41:39,000
He hasn't seen me for two weeks now.

934
00:41:39,150 --> 00:41:40,440
He must have missed me.

935
00:41:40,880 --> 00:41:41,630
Besides,

936
00:41:42,190 --> 00:41:43,760
he might discover the truth.

937
00:41:44,480 --> 00:41:46,280
So you're planning
to hide this from him?

938
00:41:47,400 --> 00:41:48,630
As a parent,

939
00:41:49,480 --> 00:41:51,590
if I can't shield my son from the storm,

940
00:41:52,320 --> 00:41:54,760
the least I can do is not hold him back.

941
00:41:57,110 --> 00:41:59,150
I have to do better than my mom did.

942
00:42:02,000 --> 00:42:02,670
Qian,

943
00:42:04,630 --> 00:42:06,000
I'll say it for the last time.

944
00:42:08,480 --> 00:42:10,280
Zhu is really nice to you.

945
00:42:11,190 --> 00:42:11,960
Maybe the three

946
00:42:12,000 --> 00:42:12,880
of you could still live

947
00:42:13,000 --> 00:42:14,070
happily together someday.

948
00:42:14,630 --> 00:42:15,440
Why does it have

949
00:42:15,590 --> 00:42:16,800
to be the three of us?

950
00:42:17,440 --> 00:42:18,550
I lived quite happily

951
00:42:18,550 --> 00:42:20,000
on my own before.

952
00:42:20,670 --> 00:42:22,630
And now I'm even happier
because I can see

953
00:42:23,070 --> 00:42:24,230
my son more often.

954
00:42:25,360 --> 00:42:26,960
I don't want you to regret it
when you get old.

955
00:42:27,510 --> 00:42:28,880
I won't regret it.

956
00:42:29,590 --> 00:42:31,710
Actually, I didn't marry Zhu

957
00:42:32,150 --> 00:42:33,760
just for money back then.

958
00:42:34,480 --> 00:42:35,880
It was mutual consent.

959
00:42:36,320 --> 00:42:37,150
Still,

960
00:42:37,480 --> 00:42:38,230
there really

961
00:42:38,440 --> 00:42:40,000
wasn't any love between us.

962
00:42:41,070 --> 00:42:44,030
Working in the construction-site
canteen was too lonely

963
00:42:46,590 --> 00:42:47,550
and exhausting.

964
00:42:48,550 --> 00:42:49,920
We were both just empty inside.
